      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been perfectly maintained and looks brand new, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
