    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six engine. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a linear power delivery to its 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement using ARP hardware. The chassis integrity is preserved with reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a pristine underside free of galvanic corrosion. Equipped with the Competition Package\u2019s quicker steering rack and cross-drilled rotors, this vehicle offers a pure, analog driving experience in concours condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
