    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that redefines what it means to be in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, seeing asphalt only on the clearest of days. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks or stone chips, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the factory-fresh scent still lingers. Every toggle, screen, and button functions with the crisp tactile feedback of a brand-new car. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by certified specialists with no expense spared. All original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive binder of maintenance records are included. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality, this is an irreplaceable find.",
      "price": 48500.0,
